    title: 'What Neuroimaging Can and Cannot Prove in Traumatic Brain Injury Litigation',
    metaDescription: "Understanding what neuroimaging can and cannot prove in TBI litigation helps attorneys build stronger cases. Learn which imaging modalities matter and when expert testimony fills the gap.",
    date: '2026-03-07',
